item.title: Garlands
item.description: Garlands are beautiful as a focal point at events. Help take your cake/food table to the next level with this design. So many different sizes and styles with garlands!

item.title: Columns & Walls
item.description: Columns make a great statement at the entrance to any event. Walls, are perfect for a photo wall backdrop.

item.title: Arches
item.description: Balloon arches look amazing at the end of a race, over a swimming pool or just about anywhere.
